**Reverse-Side Formula**

Proclaimed on the [year], [month], first day, and [hour] of the Great Year.
Supreme Illuminating Cloud, Absorbing-Light Perfected Jade Treasury Yellow Register,
petitioning for the intent herein, respectfully following
the *Supreme Celestial-Strategy Sutra*,
to guide and present [the deceased] to the Blessed Courts,
contemplating the spirit and nurturing qi,
ascending to the Cinnabar Scenery.

**Majestic, Radiant, Perfect, Wondrous, Divine Refinement, Absorbing Sutra, Prosperous Illumination**—[personal] taboo name of the spirit.
The Right Register is conferred upon the soul of [name],
commanding transcendence,
strategizing qi to congeal in the void,
soaring into the Supreme Mystery,
storing purity and dispersing turbidity,
expansively circulating wondrous mystery,
departing the dark paths,
ascending to Jade Capital.
All in accordance with the primordial descent—
swiftly executed.

Proclaimed on the [year], [month], first day, and [hour] of the Great Year.
Your subordinate, [name], bearing the decree, respectfully executes.
[List of masters’ titles.]

*Numinous Treasure Mystic Capital Jade Capital Precious Register*
Written in vermilion on azure paper,
refining and delivering, gathering form—
proclaimed and executed.

According to [location] and [name], together with the assembled participants,
reverently encountering the season of Mid-Yuan’s universal grace,
they have cultivated and honored the Great Numinous Treasure Fast and Offering.
Ascending and delivering the ancestral spirits of each household,
rescuing and transcending the sunken and stagnant souls of the dark,
they humbly implore the True Talismanic Precious Sigils—
communicating the primordial, attaining the wondrous,
revolving the mystery’s essence,
circulating through the Cinnabar Scenery.
Elevating the spirit-souls to the immortal realms,
dissolving defilement in the dark capital.
Issuing the command and disseminating the execution,
bearing the talisman for transcendence—
all in accordance with the proclaimed mandate.

**Spirits of the Body:**
Spirit of the Brain, Lord Azure Florescence;
Spirit of the Eyes, Lord Penetrating Radiance;
Spirit of the Tongue, Lord Primordial Illumination;
Spirit of the Nose, Lord Central Splendor;
Spirit of the Ears, Lord Correct Cinnabar;
Spirit of the Marrow, Lord Primordial Perfection;
Spirit of the Meridians, Lord Blended Reclusion;
Spirit of the Heart, Lord Correct Primordial;
Spirit of the Liver, Lord General Manifestation;
Spirit of the Lungs, Lord Supreme Florescence;
Spirit of the Spleen, Lord Internal Revolution;
Spirit of the Kidneys, Lord Supreme Abyss;
Spirit of the Hands, Lord Establishing Primordial;
Spirit of the Feet, Lord Preserving Guardianship;
Spirit of the Bones, Lord Absorbing Transformation;
Spirit of the Blood, Lord Flowing Harmony;
Spirit of the Limbs, Lord Primordial Vigilance;
Lord of the Supreme Abyss, Chapter of Clarity;
Spirit of the Large Intestine, Lord Guiding Script;
Spirit of the Small Intestine, Lord Prosperous Transformation;
Spirit of the Grain Path, Lord Eternal Bell;
Spirit of the Skin, Lord Enveloping Primordial;
Spirit of the Hair, Lord Circulating Numinosity;
Spirit of the Womb, Lord Flourishing Contention;
Spirit of the Stomach, Lord Penetrating Essence;
Spirit of the Membranes, Lord Self-Generation;
Spirit of the Hair (on head), Lord Transforming Prosperity;
Spirit of the Teeth, Lord Celebrating Attainment;
Spirit of the Black (pupil), Lord Internal Refinement;
Spirit of the Fluids, Lord Primordial Transformation;
Spirit of the Hun-soul, Lord Yang Essence;
Spirit of the Po-soul, Lord Summoning Yao.

The Right [Register] receives
the Emperor’s decreed talisman,
in accordance with the *Mystic Capital Jade Capital*
and the Supreme Jade Celestial Dao Lord’s Numinous Treasure Superior Command,
conferred upon the Lords of the Nine Heavens’ Generation and Transformation.
By this sacred power,
may the delivered souls of the deceased and the dark spirits,
riding this talismanic mandate,
attain clarity and correctness of spirit-soul,
eternal preservation of the ten thousand qi,
avoidance of suffering and affliction,
radiant illumination of the body;
before the Five Emperors of the Three Realms,
they shall be listed in the Upper Clarity.
*Swiftly, swiftly, in accordance with the Numinous Treasure Cavern Chapter and Statutes!*

Proclaimed on the [year], [month], first day, and [hour] of the Great Year.
Your subordinate, [name], bearing the decree, respectfully executes.
[List of masters’ titles.]

**Appended Later to the Sacred Ranks:**
Your subordinate, Zhuang, the Ten-Thousand-Transformations Nine Perfected Jade Immortal Sagely Mother, Primordial Lady of the Great Simplicity.
Your subordinate, Wei, the Lofty Primordial Purple Vacuity Celestial Illumination Lady.
Mystic Triune Numinous Dao Lord, Yellow Register Institute Envoy.
Mystic Dual August Dao Lord, Yellow Register Institute Envoy.
Mystic Primordial Radiant Dao Lord, Yellow Register Institute Envoy.

*Numinous Treasure Flying Dawn Immortal Transformation Golden Register*
Written in vermilion talismanic script on yellow paper,
regardless of size, used for posthumous cultivation—
conferred upon the deceased soul.
From the petition’s intent to the completion of expiation,
all is memorialized to the Celestial Court,
proclaiming and descending the Golden Register.
